  "instructions": [
    "1. In a large mortar, pound the chilies, garlic, and peanuts until well combined.",
    "2. Add the shredded papaya, tomatoes, fish sauce, palm sugar, and vinegar to the mortar.",
    "3. Pound the mixture until it's well combined and the papaya is slightly mashed.",
    "4. Taste and adjust the seasoning with salt as needed.",
    "5. Transfer the salad to a serving dish and garnish with chopped cilantro.",
